Property.Name: BodyScript
Property.Value:
BEGIN IF EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM [dbo].[Client] WHERE ClientName = @ClientName AND IsActive = 1) BEGIN SELECT C.ClientId,C.ClientName,D.DatabaseName,D.Connectionstring FROM [dbo].[Client] C INNER JOIN [dbo].[DatabaseDetail] D ON D.ClientId = C.CLientId AND C.IsActive = 1 AND D.IsActive = 1 WHERE C.ClientName = @clientName SET @Result ='001' END ELSE BEGIN SET @Result = '002' END
END
